Enkisisa e Yerusalem


1  Atishipe pee aajoki ninche,

“Maape enkaji o Laitoriani!”


2  Eitasheito nkejek ang too nchomito inono,

iyie Yerusalem!


3  Yerusalem, nateshetaki anaa enkanasa,

nateshetuaki meibung'ayu te nebo,


4  naa ninye eilep iloshon aapuo,

lelo oshon lo Laitoriani,

anaa apa enaitanapaki Israel,

pee eisho enkarna o Laitoriani enashe.


5  Eirragieki ilorikan le nkiguana te ine,

lelo orikan le nkitoo le nkaji e Daudi.


6  Entoomon te nkaraki eseriani e Yerusalem!

“Metubula lelo likinyor iyie!


7  Meeu eseriani isunta inono,

nelotu erripoto atua iltaleta inono!”


8  Ore too lalashera laainei o le ncholuek ai,

ajo nanu, “Metijing'a eseriani atua iyie!”


9  Ore te nkaraki enkaji o Laitoriani Enkai ang,

ekaing'oru nanu esupatisho ino.

